          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04241'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030311_WH_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-annabelle-ewing' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0401P0_20030311_WH_21' title='Link to this speech by Ms Annabelle Ewing' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
